员错过接球机会？</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VuIlvyvCFqluQyFkWgj9535PECw=/0x60:2051x1427/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73396816 /Screenshot_2024_06_08_at_5.21.35_PM.0.png&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;lQ3756&quot;>;在昨晚的美国职业棒球大联盟电视直播中&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/ 22/23651748/apple-friday-night-baseball-require-subscription&quot;>;在 Apple TV Plus&lt;/a>; 上，一个滚地球从洛杉矶道奇队球员恩里克·“基凯”·埃尔南德斯的右手弹起，直接落入他的胯部。这给了纽约洋基队击球手格莱伯·托雷斯足够的时间获得第一。这种情况经常发生吗？当然。只是事情发生时埃尔南德斯正在接受采访。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rzZvhp&quot;>;比赛播音员 Dontrelle Willis 刚刚向戴着双向麦克风的埃尔南德斯询问了球队的近况——当托雷斯将球击向三垒时，关系就变得紧密了。埃尔南德斯跑去接球，只是错误地判断了球的弹跳方式。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/40301034/dodgers-enrique-hernandez-makes-error-game-television-interview&quot;>;ESPN&lt;em>;&lt;/em>;据报道&lt;/a>;，赛后被问及采访是否与错误有关时，埃尔南德斯说，...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2024/6/8/24174447/mlb-baseball-in-game-interview-live-apple-tv-kike-hernandez-dodgers-yankees&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/8/24174447/mlb-baseball-in-game-interview-live-apple-tv-kike-hernandez-dodgers-yankees" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/8/24174447/mlb-baseball-in-game-interview-live-apple-tv-kike-hernandez-dodgers-yankees</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-08T15:06:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-08T15:06:15-04:00</updated><title>洛根在《死侍与金刚狼》第三部预告片中非常恼火</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;死侍和金刚狼抬头看着镜头后面的东西的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2KC3-6iOAhOHe60t8KBSxcR6DtU=/200x0:1229x686/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73396576/Deadpool_wolverine.0.png&quot; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;《死侍与金刚狼》中的死侍和金刚狼&lt;/em>;金刚狼。 |屏幕截图：YouTube&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;D201Ak&quot;>;几乎没有任何迹象&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24137038/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-sleeves- cassandra-nova&quot;>;在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/11/24070042/deadpool-and-wolverine-super-bowl-2024-trailer&quot;的预告片中&lt;/a>; >;&lt;em>;死侍与死侍金刚狼&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/em>;到目前为止，当金刚狼对《死侍》进行任何第四次打破多元宇宙恶作剧时，除了厌恶和恼怒之外，什么也没有。随着时间的推移，休·杰克曼的脸越来越粗糙，似乎更适合代表洛根。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5AZjUG&quot;>;新预告片更倾向于一点一滴。 - 比前两个衬垫。也许这是因为漫威和迪士尼已经设定了电影的情感赌注，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/2/11/24070042/deadpool-and-wolverine-super-bowl-2024- Trailer&quot;>;首先是《死侍》&lt;/a>;（瑞恩·雷诺兹），&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24137038/deadpool-and-wolverine-trailer-sleeves-cassandra-nova&quot;>;然后是《金刚狼》 &lt;/a>;。这全是鸡巴笑话，还有一个脾气暴躁的杰克曼，他皱着眉头，怒目而视，怒目而视。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;bq9RRy&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;gallery:12351752&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;KxG4tY&quot;>;这“不是《死侍 3》&lt;em>;，...&lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/6/8/24174358/deadpool-wolverine-trailer-3-marvel-hugh-jackman-ryan-reynolds-x-men&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/8/24174358/deadpool-wolverine-trailer-3-marvel-hugh-jackman-ryan-reynolds-x-men" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/8/24174358/deadpool-wolverine-trailer-3-marvel-hugh-jackman-ryan-reynolds-x-men</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-08T13:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-08T13:00:00-04:00</updated><title> Wholesome Direct 2024 年最可爱的游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;视频游戏 Lost and Found Co. 的屏幕截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/kFbzq-GwYWn4vCnR2Y8gu7wKd5Q=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73396410/LostAndFoundCo_Screenshot_07.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;失物招领公司&lt;/em>; |图片：Bit Egg&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;yRVn2t&quot;>;尽管它&lt;a hre